comment: Sweet & woody with notes of coffee and stewed fruit on the nose. Sweet, fiery and a little bitey on the palate with tastes of rich dark chocolate, fudge and a hint of salty air. Heavy, creamy mouthfeel with a medium, sinking finish.

Smagt 2010:
Lækker rund sødme, prikker lidt, ikke-røget,

Eye: light yellow, thick
Nose: light, sweet, citrus?
Pallet: sweet, strong
Finish: peach, medium length?
